sentences.en: Angel : Oh yeah , I see. Isn't this place beautiful, Katie?
sentences.cn: 哦, 我看到了. 这个地方可真是漂亮啊,对不对, 凯蒂?

sentences.en: But Katie, my older sister, is not there.
sentences.cn: 但是凯蒂，我的姐姐，她不在那里。

sentences.en: By the way, will you take little Katie with you ?
sentences.cn: 顺便问一下, 你带凯蒂一起去 吗 ?

sentences.en: D . Katie tried to kill herself order to reach out for help.
sentences.cn: 凯蒂是为了寻求帮助而试图杀害自己.

sentences.en: Hi, I'm Katie Couric , welcome to Eye to Eye.
sentences.cn: 大家好, 我是凯蒂库里克.欢迎收看面对面.

sentences.en: Katie Moore took the ladies' side-saddle award.
sentences.cn: 凯蒂·穆尔获得了最佳女侧骑手奖。

sentences.en: Katie nodded so hard I feared for her cervical vertebrae.
sentences.cn: Katie拼命地点头,这让我担心她的颈椎.

sentences.en: Katie will not be clapping for me when I finally get my college diploma or giving me advice on my wedding day.
sentences.cn: 在我拿到大学文凭那一刻，再也不会有凯蒂为我鼓掌了，在我结婚那天，她也不能从旁给我任何意见。

sentences.en: Katie, along with Alicia and Angelina, joined the DA ( OP 17 ).
sentences.cn: 凯蒂跟艾丽娅、安吉利娜一起加入了DA组织 ( 凤凰社第十七章 ).

sentences.en: Katie: Yes, Daniel is a good kisser, I really enjoyed it.
sentences.cn: 梁凯蒂: 是的, 丹尼尔是个亲吻的高手, 我很满意.

sentences.en: Later that day I was horsing around with Katie when she accidentally stuck her finger in my eye.
sentences.cn: 那天晚些时候，我正和凯蒂一起胡闹时，她不小心用手指戳到了我的一只眼睛。

sentences.en: Mark says the ideas are Katie's own, and is quick to praise her talent.
sentences.cn: 马克说这些都是凯蒂自己的想法，并随即称赞起她的天赋来。

sentences.en: S : yes, his marriage to Katie is actually quite scandalous.
sentences.cn: 是啊.他跟凯蒂结婚简直是个笑话.

sentences.en: She’d ask me about my girlfriend, Katie, what we did on our dates, whether I said nice things to her.
sentences.cn: 她问起我的女朋友凯蒂，问我们约会时都做些什么，以及我是否对她说过好听的。

sentences.en: So katie, first of all, what drove these prices up so high in the first place?
sentences.cn: 那么,Katie, 首先, 为什么刚开始的时候价格涨的这么高?

sentences.en: When was the last time you saw Katie Markum?
sentences.cn: 你最后见到凯蒂马库是什么时候?

sentences.en: You mean to tell me , Katie Scarlett O'Hara , that land doesn't mean anything to you?
sentences.cn: 你是说, 斯佳丽, 你不爱惜你的田地 吗 ?

sentences.en: You need sleep and Katie Scarlett is here, so you need not worry about anything.
sentences.cn: 你需要睡了,让凯帝-思嘉留在这里, 这样你就什么都不用操心了.
